trans-unit.source: Represents the collection of values in a <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2" />.
trans-unit.target: 表示 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2" /> 中值的集合。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別無法被繼承。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.Values%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property returns an instance of this type, containing all the values in that <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.Values%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性會傳回包含的所有值，這個型別執行個體<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602>。

trans-unit.source: The order of the values in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection> is unspecified, but it is the same order as the associated keys in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.KeyCollection> returned by the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.Keys%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property.
trans-unit.target: 雖然 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection> 中值的順序並未指定，但此順序會與 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.KeyCollection> 屬性傳回之 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.Keys%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 中關聯索引鍵的順序相同。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection> is not a static copy; instead, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection> refers back to the values in the original <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection>不是靜態的複本; 相反地，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection>中原始的值是指回<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602>。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, changes to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602> continue to be reflected in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，變更為<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602>才會反映在繼續<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection>。

trans-unit.source: Public static (<see langword="Shared" /> in Visual Basic) members of this type are thread safe.
trans-unit.target: 公用靜態 (<see langword="Shared" />在 Visual Basic 中) 這種類型的成員都具備執行緒安全。

trans-unit.source: Any instance members are not guaranteed to be thread safe.
trans-unit.target: 不保證任何執行個體成員是安全執行緒。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" /> can support multiple readers concurrently, as long as the collection is not modified.
trans-unit.target: A<see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" />可以支援多個讀取器同時，只要未修改集合。

trans-unit.source: Even so, enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: 即便如此，列舉集合在本質上並非安全執行緒程序。

trans-unit.source: To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 若要確保列舉期間的執行緒安全性，您可以在整個列舉期間鎖定集合。

trans-unit.source: To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要讓多重執行緒能夠存取集合以便進行讀取和寫入，您必須實作自己的同步處理。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2" /> whose values are reflected in the new <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2" />，其值反映在新 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" /> 中。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" /> class that reflects the values in the specified <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2" />.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" /> 類別的新執行個體，反映指定 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2" /> 中的值。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection> is not a static copy; instead, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection> refers back to the values in the original <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection>不是靜態的複本; 相反地，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection>中原始的值是指回<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602>。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, changes to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602> continue to be reflected in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，變更為<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602>才會反映在繼續<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection>。

trans-unit.source: This constructor is an O(1) operation.
trans-unit.target: 這個建構函式是 o （1） 運算。

trans-unit.target: <paramref name="dictionary" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" /> that is the destination of the elements copied from <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 一維 <see cref="T:System.Array" />，是從 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" /> 複製過來之項目的目的端。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Array" /> must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Array" /> 必須有以零為起始的索引。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: <c>array</c> 中以零起始的索引，複製作業從此處開始。

trans-unit.source: Copies the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" /> elements to an existing one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" />, starting at the specified array index.
trans-unit.target: 從指定的陣列索引處開始，複製 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" /> 項目至現有一維 <see cref="T:System.Array" />。

trans-unit.source: The elements are copied to the <xref:System.Array> in the same order in which the enumerator iterates through the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection>.
trans-unit.target: 將元素複製到<xref:System.Array>以相同的順序，以列舉值逐一<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection>。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(`n`) operation, where `n` is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法是 O (`n`) 作業，其中`n`是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 小於零。

trans-unit.source: The number of elements in the source <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" /> is greater than the available space from <paramref name="index" /> to the end of the destination <paramref name="array" />.
trans-unit.target: 來源 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" /> 中的項目數目，大於 <paramref name="index" /> 到目的 <paramref name="array" /> 結尾的可用空間。

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of elements contained in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 取得 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" /> 中所包含的項目數。

trans-unit.source: The number of elements contained in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" /> 中所包含的項目數。

trans-unit.source: Retrieving the value of this property is an O(1) operation.
trans-unit.target: 擷取這個屬性的值是一種 O(1) 運算。

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator that iterates through the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 傳回在 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" /> 中逐一查看的列舉值。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection.Enumerator" /> for the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection.Enumerator" /> 的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.ValueCollection" />。

trans-unit.source: The `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in C++, `For Each` in Visual Basic) hides the complexity of enumerators.
trans-unit.target: `foreach` C# 語言的陳述式 (`for each` c + +`For Each`在 Visual Basic 中) 會隱藏列舉值的複雜度。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, using `foreach` is recommended, instead of directly manipulating the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 因此，建議您使用 `foreach`，而不要直接使用列舉值。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators can be used to read the data in the collection, but they cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式可以用來讀取集合中的資料，但是無法用來修改基礎集合。

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 一開始，列舉程式位在集合中的第一個項目之前。

trans-unit.source: At this position, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 在這個位置上，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> 並未定義。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，在讀取 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> 的值之前，必須呼叫 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> 以將列舉值前移至集合的第一個項目。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> returns the same object until <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> 會傳回相同的物件直到呼叫 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> sets <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> to the next element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> 會將 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> 設定為下一個項目。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> passes the end of the collection, the enumerator is positioned after the last element in the collection and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>超過集合的列舉值的結尾會位於集合中的最後一個元素之後和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: When the enumerator is at this position, subsequent calls to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> also return `false`.
trans-unit.target: 列舉值位於這個位置上，後續呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>也會傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: If the last call to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果最後一個呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A>是未定義。

trans-unit.source: You cannot set <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> to the first element of the collection again; you must create a new enumerator instance instead.
trans-unit.target: 您不能再次將 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.ValueCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> 設定為集合的第一個項目；您必須建立新的列舉值執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 只要集合維持不變，列舉程式就持續有效。

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying, or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated and its behavior is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果對集合進行變更，例如加入、修改或刪除項目，列舉程式會永久失效，且其行為未定義。

trans-unit.source: The enumerator does not have exclusive access to the collection; therefore, enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式沒有集合的獨佔存取權，因此，列舉集合內容本質上並不是安全的執行緒程序。

trans-unit.source: To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 若要確保列舉期間的執行緒安全性，您可以在整個列舉期間鎖定集合。

trans-unit.source: To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要讓多重執行緒能夠存取集合以便進行讀取和寫入，您必須實作自己的同步處理。

trans-unit.source: Default implementations of collections in <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> are not synchronized.
trans-unit.target: 集合中的預設實作<xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType>未同步處理。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(1) operation.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法是一種 o （1） 運算。

trans-unit.target: 要加入至 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection`1" /> 的物件。

trans-unit.source: This implementation always throws <see cref="T:System.NotSupportedException" />.
trans-unit.target: 這個實作一律會擲回 <see cref="T:System.NotSupportedException" />。

trans-unit.source: This implementation always throws <see cref="T:System.NotSupportedException" />.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection`1" /> contains a specific value.
trans-unit.target: 判斷 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection`1" /> 是否包含特定值。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="item" /> is found in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection`1" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果在 <see langword="true" /> 中找到 <paramref name="item" />，則為 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection`1" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Implementations can vary in how they determine equality of objects; for example, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> uses <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A>, whereas, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602> allows the user to specify the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IComparer%601> implementation to use for comparing keys.
trans-unit.target: 實作依判斷物件相等的方法會有所不同；例如，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> 使用 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A>，而 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602> 則讓使用者指定要用來比較索引鍵的 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IComparer%601> 實作。

trans-unit.source: A collection that is read-only does not allow the addition, removal, or modification of elements after the collection is created.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> returns the same object until <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> 會傳回相同的物件直到呼叫 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> sets <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> to the next element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> 會將 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> 設定為下一個項目。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> passes the end of the collection, the enumerator is positioned after the last element in the collection and <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>超過集合的列舉值的結尾會位於集合中的最後一個元素之後和<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: When the enumerator is at this position, subsequent calls to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> also return `false`.
trans-unit.target: 列舉值位於這個位置上，後續呼叫<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>也會傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: If the last call to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果最後一個呼叫<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A>是未定義。

trans-unit.source: You cannot set <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> to the first element of the collection again; you must create a new enumerator instance instead.
trans-unit.target: 您不能再次將 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> 設定為集合的第一個項目；您必須建立新的列舉值執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 只要集合維持不變，列舉程式就持續有效。

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying, or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated and its behavior is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果對集合進行變更，例如加入、修改或刪除項目，列舉程式會永久失效，且其行為未定義。

trans-unit.source: The enumerator does not have exclusive access to the collection; therefore, enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式沒有集合的獨佔存取權，因此，列舉集合內容本質上並不是安全的執行緒程序。

trans-unit.source: To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 若要確保列舉期間的執行緒安全性，您可以在整個列舉期間鎖定集合。

trans-unit.source: To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要讓多重執行緒能夠存取集合以便進行讀取和寫入，您必須實作自己的同步處理。

trans-unit.source: Default implementations of collections in <xref:System.Collections.Generic> are not synchronized.
trans-unit.target: 集合中的預設實作<xref:System.Collections.Generic>未同步處理。

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator that iterates through a collection.
trans-unit.target: 傳回逐一查看集合的列舉值。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" />，可用於逐一查看集合。

trans-unit.source: The `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in C++, `For Each` in Visual Basic) hides the complexity of the enumerators.
trans-unit.target: `foreach` C# 語言的陳述式 (`for each` c + +`For Each`在 Visual Basic 中) 會隱藏列舉值的複雜度。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, using `foreach` is recommended, instead of directly manipulating the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 因此，建議您使用 `foreach`，而不要直接使用列舉值。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators can be used to read the data in the collection, but they cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式可以用來讀取集合中的資料，但是無法用來修改基礎集合。

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 一開始，列舉程式位在集合中的第一個項目之前。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> also brings the enumerator back to this position.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> 也會將列舉值帶回至這個位置。

trans-unit.source: At this position, <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 在這個位置上，<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> 並未定義。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，在讀取 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> 的值之前，必須呼叫 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> 以將列舉值前移至集合的第一個項目。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> returns the same object until either <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> or <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> 會傳回相同的物件直到呼叫 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> 或 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> sets <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> to the next element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> 會將 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> 設定為下一個項目。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> passes the end of the collection, the enumerator is positioned after the last element in the collection and <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>超過集合的列舉值的結尾會位於集合中的最後一個元素之後和<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: When the enumerator is at this position, subsequent calls to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> also return `false`.
trans-unit.target: 列舉值位於這個位置上，後續呼叫<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>也會傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: If the last call to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果最後一個呼叫<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`，<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>是未定義。

trans-unit.source: To set <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> to the first element of the collection again, you can call <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> followed by <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 若要再次將 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> 設定為集合的第一個元素，您可以在呼叫 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> 之後，接著呼叫 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 只要集合維持不變，列舉程式就持續有效。

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying, or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated and its behavior is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果對集合進行變更，例如加入、修改或刪除項目，列舉程式會永久失效，且其行為未定義。
